ormal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"> {</span></font></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">// KFH added</font></span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: italic;">PrintWriter</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"> out = </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">response</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">.</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(33, 150, 255);">getWriter</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">();</span></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">out.</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">print</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">("You have clicked on MyWebServlet action!");</span></font></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">}</font></span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">Note: You will see an error sign on the left side. Just click and choose </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">Import 'PrinterWriter' (</span><a href="http://java.io" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">java.io</a><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">) </span></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><br /></font></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">Step 6. Now we need to create a JSP file:</font></span></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">Click on "WebContent" --&gt; New --&gt; JSP File  and give a name "index"  ( WEB-INF/web.xml looks as a default for such names)</font></span></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">--&gt; Next  leave the default options.</font></span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><br /></font></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">Step 7. Edit the index.jsp file</font></span></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">&lt;body&gt;</font></span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">&lt;h1&gt;</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"> This is my first Dynamic Application ever written </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">&lt;/h1&gt;</span></font></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">&lt;hr/&gt;</font></span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">&lt;form</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"> action="MyWebServlet"</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">&gt;</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"></span></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">&lt;input</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"> type="submit" value="Click Me"</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"> /&gt;</span></font></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">&lt;/form&gt;</font></span></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">&lt;/body&gt;</font></span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><br /></font></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">Step 8: Publishing the Application</font></span></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">Right click on "MyWebApp" and "Run As " --&gt; "On Server"</font></span></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"><font style="font-size: 18px;">That's it !!!</font></span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><br /></font></div><div><br /></div></en-note>